- docs_control_center/DEV_RULES_AI_FIRST.md
- docs_control_center/FIELD_REGISTRY.md
- docs_control_center/README_HACKATHON_CHARGER.md 或 docs_control_center/README_ECOMMERCE_INVENTORY.md（按当前任务选）
